- Not too little (showing good faith)

Common approaches:
- Send $2-3 (40-60% of endowment) as a trust-building gesture
- This creates $6-9 for the trustee to work with
- If they return fairly, both can benefit

I'll send $3 as a reasonable initial trust signal. This:
